headline: Netflix–Warner Bros. deal: 6 things to keep an eye on
summary: Netflix (NFLX) announced it has reached a deal to buy Warner Bros. (WBD). Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi outlines six key aspects of the deal that he's paying particular attention to. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Opening Bid.
